{"tid":42304,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"已經五日無洗頭了...","createTime":"2016-12-16T14:36:54.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-16T15:34:38.000Z","uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8b69e3740c38f1c1ad7e94d7b3dede7aa57894d5","tid":42304,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T14:36:54.000Z","msg":"呢排放緊假，<br />\n又無人約，<br />\n差不多成個禮拜留起屋企，<br />\n五日無洗過頭，<br />\n但係我竟然上左癮！！！<br />\n<br />\n得閒用手指捽下Ｄ頭皮再閒下，<br />\n陣味真係好吸引到我！！！<br />\n<br />\n同埋，當你試過幾日唔洗頭之後，<br />\n會有種心癮想keep住唔洗落去，<br />\n呢種動力比起戒Ｊ真係強好多倍！！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/12.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f051cb92572851cb1b0941b6144ca3f984353eb","tid":42304,"uid":66494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T14:51:25.000Z","msg":"臭肥宅"},{"pid":"55769036f989bbcc9d3d9d17b794df30c6e1fb93","tid":42304,"uid":10340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T14:52:37.000Z","msg":"個頭唔痕咩？"},{"pid":"38dda2ef8fc8407da0f200ea6364348ce297454b","tid":42304,"uid":6908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T14:53:44.000Z","msg":"D油要燒熱佢先炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee05d760cea92281e8fe8ce6b4d6bd3af79a3159","tid":42304,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T15:03:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>臭肥宅</blockquote><br />\n收皮啦，我美國隊長咁嘅身型架"},{"pid":"f14bf7daf87b420c72bc153273423d8bb0f98e93","tid":42304,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-